                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12933990" author="jhermes" created="Fri, 19 Nov 2010 21:37:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Similar to the patch for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1527&quot; title=&quot;ensure compaction thresholds are sane&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-1527&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-1527&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, this validates the creation of ColumnDefs from YAML and then from thrift/avro.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For simplicity, both name and index need to be set or unset at the same time. I don&apos;t think anyone is complaining that it&apos;s too hard to introduce non-obvious bugs, so I&apos;m being explicit here.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12934003" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 19 Nov 2010 21:57:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks like you got a little too clever with the xors &amp;#8211; index_type set but index_name not, is valid.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12934032" author="jhermes" created="Fri, 19 Nov 2010 22:39:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Whoops, I read CFMD:279 wrong. I thought it was a bug that we were auto-generating the name incorrectly. Back to previous logic.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12934498" author="jhermes" created="Mon, 22 Nov 2010 16:08:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1761&quot; title=&quot;Indexes: Auto-generating the CFname may collide with user-generated names&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-1761&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-1761&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is the bug that I originally caught and is separate from this one.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12934890" author="jbellis" created="Tue, 23 Nov 2010 16:57:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12970402" author="hudson" created="Sat, 11 Dec 2010 07:35:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Cassandra-0.7 #70 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://hudson.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra-0.7/70/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://hudson.apache.org/hudson/job/Cassandra-0.7/70/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
